  H \vert 0 \rangle & =
  \begin{pmatrix}
    \frac{1}{\sqrt{2}} & \frac{1}{\sqrt{2}} \\[2mm]
    \frac{1}{\sqrt{2}} & -\frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}
  \end{pmatrix}
  \begin{pmatrix}
    1\\[2mm]
    0
  \end{pmatrix}
  = \begin{pmatrix}
    \frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}\\[2mm]
    \frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}
  \end{pmatrix}
  = \vert + \rangle\\[6mm]
  H \vert 1 \rangle
  & =
  \begin{pmatrix}
    \frac{1}{\sqrt{2}} & \frac{1}{\sqrt{2}} \\[2mm]
    \frac{1}{\sqrt{2}} & -\frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}
  \end{pmatrix}
  \begin{pmatrix}
    0\\[2mm]
    1
  \end{pmatrix}
  = \begin{pmatrix}
    \frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}\\[2mm]
    -\frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}
  \end{pmatrix}
  = \vert - \rangle\\[6mm]
  H \vert + \rangle
  & =
  \begin{pmatrix}
    \frac{1}{\sqrt{2}} & \frac{1}{\sqrt{2}} \\[2mm]
    \frac{1}{\sqrt{2}} & -\frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}
  \end{pmatrix}
  \begin{pmatrix}
    \frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}\\[2mm]
    \frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}
  \end{pmatrix}
  = \begin{pmatrix}
    1\\[2mm]
    0
  \end{pmatrix}
  = \vert 0 \rangle\\[6mm]
  H \vert - \rangle
  & =
  \begin{pmatrix}
    \frac{1}{\sqrt{2}} & \frac{1}{\sqrt{2}} \\[2mm]
    \frac{1}{\sqrt{2}} & -\frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}
  \end{pmatrix}
  \begin{pmatrix}
    \frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}\\[2mm]
    -\frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}
  \end{pmatrix}
  = \begin{pmatrix}
    0\\[2mm]
    1
  \end{pmatrix}
  = \vert 1 \rangle
